msgstr "It’s not easy for someone with delusion to teach this.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya20, sc32
msgctxt "mn95:20.1"
msgid "Yato naṃ samannesamāno visuddhaṃ mohanīyehi dhammehi samanupassati; "
msgstr "Scrutinizing them in this way they see that they are purified of qualities that promote delusion. "

#. VAR: dhatānaṃ → dhāritānaṃ (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "mn95:20.2"
msgid "atha tamhi saddhaṃ niveseti, saddhājāto upasaṅkamati, upasaṅkamanto payirupāsati, payirupāsanto sotaṃ odahati, ohitasoto dhammaṃ suṇāti, sutvā dhammaṃ dhāreti, dhatānaṃ dhammānaṃ atthaṃ upaparikkhati, atthaṃ upaparikkhato dhammā nijjhānaṃ khamanti, dhammanijjhānakkhantiyā sati chando jāyati, chandajāto ussahati, ussahitvā tuleti, tulayitvā padahati, pahitatto samāno kāyena ceva paramasaccaṃ sacchikaroti paññāya ca naṃ ativijjha passati. "
msgstr "Next, they place faith in them. When faith has arisen they approach the teacher. They pay homage, lend an ear, hear the teachings, remember the teachings, reflect on their meaning, and accept them after consideration. Then enthusiasm springs up; they make an effort, weigh up, and persevere. Persevering, they directly realize the ultimate truth, and see it with penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "mn95:20.3"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, bhāradvāja, saccānubodho hoti, ettāvatā saccamanubujjhati, ettāvatā ca mayaṃ saccānubodhaṃ paññapema; "
msgstr "That’s how the awakening to truth is defined, Bhāradvāja. I describe the awakening to truth as defined in this way. "

msgctxt "mn95:20.4"
msgid "na tveva tāva saccānuppatti hotī”ti. "
msgstr "But this is not yet the arrival at the truth.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya21, pts-vp-pli2.174, sc33
msgctxt "mn95:21.1"
msgid "“Ettāvatā, bho gotama, saccānubodho hoti, ettāvatā saccamanubujjhati, ettāvatā ca mayaṃ saccānubodhaṃ pekkhāma. "
msgstr "“That’s how the awakening to truth is defined, Master Gotama. I regard the awakening to truth as defined in this way. "

msgctxt "mn95:21.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā pana, bho gotama, saccānuppatti hoti, kittāvatā saccamanupāpuṇāti? "
msgstr "But Master Gotama, how do you define the arrival at the truth?” "

msgctxt "mn95:21.3"
msgid "Saccānuppattiṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn95:21.4"
msgid "“Tesaṃyeva, bhāradvāja, dhammānaṃ āsevanā bhāvanā bahulīkammaṃ saccānuppatti hoti. "
msgstr "“By the cultivation, development, and making much of these very same things there is the arrival at the truth. "

msgctxt "mn95:21.5"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, bhāradvāja, saccānuppatti hoti, ettāvatā saccamanupāpuṇāti, ettāvatā ca mayaṃ saccānuppattiṃ paññapemā”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how the arrival at the truth is defined, Bhāradvāja. I describe the arrival at the truth as defined in this way.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya22, sc34
msgctxt "mn95:22.1"
msgid "“Ettāvatā, bho gotama, saccānuppatti hoti, ettāvatā saccamanupāpuṇāti, ettāvatā ca mayaṃ saccānuppattiṃ pekkhāma. "
msgstr "“That’s how the arrival at the truth is defined, Master Gotama. I regard the arrival at the truth as defined in this way. "

msgctxt "mn95:22.2"
msgid "Saccānuppattiyā pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr "But what quality is helpful for arriving at the truth?” "

msgctxt "mn95:22.3"
msgid "Saccānuppattiyā bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn95:22.4"
msgid "“Saccānuppattiyā kho, bhāradvāja, padhānaṃ bahukāraṃ. "
msgstr "“Striving is helpful for arriving at the truth. "

msgctxt "mn95:22.5"
msgid "No cetaṃ padaheyya, nayidaṃ saccamanupāpuṇeyya. "
msgstr "If you don’t strive, you won’t arrive at the truth. "

msgctxt "mn95:22.6"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho padahati tasmā saccamanupāpuṇāti. "
msgstr "You arrive at the truth because you strive. "

msgctxt "mn95:22.7"
msgid "Tasmā saccānuppattiyā padhānaṃ bahukāran”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why striving is helpful for arriving at the truth.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya23, sc35
msgctxt "mn95:23.1"
msgid "“Padhānassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr "“But what quality is helpful for striving?” "

msgctxt "mn95:23.2"
msgid "Padhānassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn95:23.3"
msgid "“Padhānassa kho, bhāradvāja, tulanā bahukārā. "
msgstr "“Weighing up the teachings is helpful for striving … "

msgctxt "mn95:23.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ tuleyya, nayidaṃ padaheyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:23.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho tuleti tasmā padahati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:23.6"
msgid "Tasmā padhānassa tulanā bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya24, sc36
msgctxt "mn95:24.1"
msgid "“Tulanāya pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:24.2"
msgid "Tulanāya bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:24.3"
msgid "“Tulanāya kho, bhāradvāja, ussāho bahukāro. "
msgstr "Making an effort is helpful for weighing up the teachings … "

msgctxt "mn95:24.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ ussaheyya, nayidaṃ tuleyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:24.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho ussahati tasmā tuleti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:24.6"
msgid "Tasmā tulanāya ussāho bahukāro”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya25, sc37
msgctxt "mn95:25.1"
msgid "“Ussāhassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:25.2"
msgid "Ussāhassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:25.3"
msgid "“Ussāhassa kho, bhāradvāja, chando bahukāro. "
msgstr "Enthusiasm is helpful for making an effort … "

msgctxt "mn95:25.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ chando jāyetha, nayidaṃ ussaheyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:25.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho chando jāyati tasmā ussahati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:25.6"
msgid "Tasmā ussāhassa chando bahukāro”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya26, pts-vp-pli2.175, sc38
msgctxt "mn95:26.1"
msgid "“Chandassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:26.2"
msgid "Chandassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:26.3"
msgid "“Chandassa kho, bhāradvāja, dhammanijjhānakkhanti bahukārā. "
msgstr "Acceptance of the teachings after consideration is helpful for enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "mn95:26.4"
msgid "No cete dhammā nijjhānaṃ khameyyuṃ, nayidaṃ chando jāyetha. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:26.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho dhammā nijjhānaṃ khamanti tasmā chando jāyati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:26.6"
msgid "Tasmā chandassa dhammanijjhānakkhanti bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya27, sc39
msgctxt "mn95:27.1"
msgid "“Dhammanijjhānakkhantiyā pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:27.2"
msgid "Dhammanijjhānakkhantiyā bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:27.3"
msgid "“Dhammanijjhānakkhantiyā kho, bhāradvāja, atthūpaparikkhā bahukārā. "
msgstr "Reflecting on the meaning of the teachings is helpful for accepting them after consideration … "

msgctxt "mn95:27.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ atthaṃ upaparikkheyya, nayidaṃ dhammā nijjhānaṃ khameyyuṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:27.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho atthaṃ upaparikkhati tasmā dhammā nijjhānaṃ khamanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:27.6"
msgid "Tasmā dhammanijjhānakkhantiyā atthūpaparikkhā bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya28, sc40
msgctxt "mn95:28.1"
msgid "“Atthūpaparikkhāya pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:28.2"
msgid "Atthūpaparikkhāya bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:28.3"
msgid "“Atthūpaparikkhāya kho, bhāradvāja, dhammadhāraṇā bahukārā. "
msgstr "Remembering the teachings is helpful for reflecting on their meaning … "

msgctxt "mn95:28.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ dhammaṃ dhāreyya, nayidaṃ atthaṃ upaparikkheyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:28.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho dhammaṃ dhāreti tasmā atthaṃ upaparikkhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:28.6"
msgid "Tasmā atthūpaparikkhāya dhammadhāraṇā bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya29, sc41
msgctxt "mn95:29.1"
msgid "“Dhammadhāraṇāya pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:29.2"
msgid "Dhammadhāraṇāya bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:29.3"
msgid "“Dhammadhāraṇāya kho, bhāradvāja, dhammassavanaṃ bahukāraṃ. "
msgstr "Hearing the teachings is helpful for remembering the teachings … "

msgctxt "mn95:29.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ dhammaṃ suṇeyya, nayidaṃ dhammaṃ dhāreyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:29.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho dhammaṃ suṇāti tasmā dhammaṃ dhāreti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:29.6"
msgid "Tasmā dhammadhāraṇāya dhammassavanaṃ bahukāran”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya30, pts-vp-pli2.176, sc42
msgctxt "mn95:30.1"
msgid "“Dhammassavanassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:30.2"
msgid "Dhammassavanassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:30.3"
msgid "“Dhammassavanassa kho, bhāradvāja, sotāvadhānaṃ bahukāraṃ. "
msgstr "Listening is helpful for hearing the teachings … "

msgctxt "mn95:30.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ sotaṃ odaheyya, nayidaṃ dhammaṃ suṇeyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:30.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho sotaṃ odahati tasmā dhammaṃ suṇāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:30.6"
msgid "Tasmā dhammassavanassa sotāvadhānaṃ bahukāran”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya31, sc43
msgctxt "mn95:31.1"
msgid "“Sotāvadhānassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:31.2"
msgid "Sotāvadhānassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:31.3"
msgid "“Sotāvadhānassa kho, bhāradvāja, payirupāsanā bahukārā. "
msgstr "Paying homage is helpful for listening … "

msgctxt "mn95:31.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ payirupāseyya, nayidaṃ sotaṃ odaheyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:31.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho payirupāsati tasmā sotaṃ odahati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:31.6"
msgid "Tasmā sotāvadhānassa payirupāsanā bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya32, sc44
msgctxt "mn95:32.1"
msgid "“Payirupāsanāya pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:32.2"
msgid "Payirupāsanāya bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:32.3"
msgid "“Payirupāsanāya kho, bhāradvāja, upasaṅkamanaṃ bahukāraṃ. "
msgstr "Approaching is helpful for paying homage … "

msgctxt "mn95:32.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ upasaṅkameyya, nayidaṃ payirupāseyya. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:32.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho upasaṅkamati tasmā payirupāsati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:32.6"
msgid "Tasmā payirupāsanāya upasaṅkamanaṃ bahukāran”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya33, sc45
msgctxt "mn95:33.1"
msgid "“Upasaṅkamanassa pana, bho gotama, katamo dhammo bahukāro? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:33.2"
msgid "Upasaṅkamanassa bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ pucchāmā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn95:33.3"
msgid "“Upasaṅkamanassa kho, bhāradvāja, saddhā bahukārā. "
msgstr "Faith is helpful for approaching a teacher. "

msgctxt "mn95:33.4"
msgid "No cetaṃ saddhā jāyetha, nayidaṃ upasaṅkameyya. "
msgstr "If you don’t give rise to faith, you won’t approach a teacher. "

msgctxt "mn95:33.5"
msgid "Yasmā ca kho saddhā jāyati tasmā upasaṅkamati. "
msgstr "You approach a teacher because you have faith. "

msgctxt "mn95:33.6"
msgid "Tasmā upasaṅkamanassa saddhā bahukārā”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why faith is helpful for approaching a teacher.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya34, pts-vp-pli2.177, sc46
msgctxt "mn95:34.1"
msgid "“Saccānurakkhaṇaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ apucchimha, saccānurakkhaṇaṃ bhavaṃ gotamo byākāsi; "
msgstr "“I’ve asked Master Gotama about the preservation of truth, and he has answered me. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.2"
msgid "tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca tena camha attamanā. "
msgstr "I like and accept this, and am satisfied with it. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.3"
msgid "Saccānubodhaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ apucchimha, saccānubodhaṃ bhavaṃ gotamo byākāsi; "
msgstr "I’ve asked Master Gotama about awakening to the truth, and he has answered me. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.4"
msgid "tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca tena camha attamanā. "
msgstr "I like and accept this, and am satisfied with it. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.5"
msgid "Saccānuppattiṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ apucchimha, saccānuppattiṃ bhavaṃ gotamo byākāsi; "
msgstr "I’ve asked Master Gotama about the arrival at the truth, and he has answered me. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.6"
msgid "tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca tena camha attamanā. "
msgstr "I like and accept this, and am satisfied with it. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.7"
msgid "Saccānuppattiyā bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ apucchimha, saccānuppattiyā bahukāraṃ dhammaṃ bhavaṃ gotamo byākāsi; "
msgstr "I’ve asked Master Gotama about the things that are helpful for the arrival at the truth, and he has answered me. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.8"
msgid "tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca tena camha attamanā. "
msgstr "I like and accept this, and am satisfied with it. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.9"
msgid "Yaṃyadeva ca mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ apucchimha taṃtadeva bhavaṃ gotamo byākāsi; "
msgstr "Whatever I have asked Master Gotama about he has answered me. "

msgctxt "mn95:34.10"
msgid "tañca panamhākaṃ ruccati ceva khamati ca tena camha attamanā. "
msgstr "I like and accept this, and am satisfied with it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn95:34.11"
msgid "Mayañhi, bho gotama, pubbe evaṃ jānāma: "
msgstr "Master Gotama, I used to think this: "

msgctxt "mn95:34.12"
msgid "‘ke ca muṇḍakā samaṇakā ibbhā kaṇhā bandhupādāpaccā, ke ca dhammassa aññātāro’ti? "
msgstr "‘Who are these shavelings, fake ascetics, riffraff, black spawn from the feet of our Kinsman to be counted alongside those who understand the teaching?’ "

msgctxt "mn95:34.13"
msgid "Ajanesi vata me bhavaṃ gotamo samaṇesu samaṇapemaṃ, samaṇesu samaṇapasādaṃ, samaṇesu samaṇagāravaṃ. "
msgstr "The Buddha has inspired me to have love, confidence, and respect for ascetics! "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya35
msgctxt "mn95:35.1"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! … "

msgctxt "mn95:35.2"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn95:35.3"
msgid "Caṅkīsuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

